properties.Name: RefiningDeviceType
properties.Description:
The type of device based on its function, common characteristics.

Ex:
- Solenoid 
- Clamp meter (current transducer)
- Wheatstone bridge (measures resistance)
- Capacitance meter (measures capacitance)
- LCR meter (measures inductance, capacitance, resistance)
- EMF Meter (measures Electric and Magnetic Fields)
- Electrometer (measures voltages)
- RF probe
- Signal tracer
- Logic analyzer (tests digital circuits)
- Spectrum analyzer (measures spectral energy of signals)
- Protocol analyzer 
- Vector signal analyzer (
- Time-domain reflectometer (Tests integrity of long cables)
- Semiconductor curve tracer
- Frequency synthesizer
- Function generator
- Digital pattern generator
- Pulse generator
- Signal injector
